5" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Characterisation of the use-wear resulting from bamboo working and its importance to address the hypothesis of the existence of a bamboo industry in prehistoric Southeast Asia.</a> Quaternary International, 416, 95-125.</li></ol>
